---
description: Release gate for AI API Ops deployments.
globs: scripts/**,package.json,public/**,src/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Do not report Done after local build only.

Required before Done:

- `npm run verify`
- `git diff` reviewed
- Cloudflare production deploy confirmed
- cache-busted production live checks pass
- changed public pages return 200
- planned pages return 404
- `sitemap.xml` returns 200 and only includes public canonical URLs
- `robots.txt` returns 200 and references `https://aiapiops.com/sitemap.xml`
- `llms.txt` returns 200 and only lists public pages
- CTA URLs exact:
  - `https://app.rutaapi.com/register?lng=en`
  - `https://app.rutaapi.com/pricing`
- no banned claims
- no cross-project contamination
- no playground copy
- no duplicate numbering patterns like `1. 1` / `2. 2` / `3. 3`
- production HTML downloaded and scanned for changed pages
